title: (digimob) Occult Mob's Submissions Digest #24
description:
Occult.digital.mobilization (digimob) brings you another submissions digest with content not included in our mega-torrents.

This torrent represents a work of LOVE. All texts so far gathered, as well as all future gatherings, aim to facilitate the studies of sincere students.

Future releases will include submissions from users like YOU.

Digimob's archive provides an invaluable service to dedicated students of the occult sciences, and a forum community has been created to provide a platform for these students to engage in respectful discourse on topics related to our releases. Digimob invites you to join our new forum community at http://digimob.tk.

For some of us, the time has come to mobilize. If you have an interest in assisting in this process - we all have strengths to bring to the table - please email occult.digital.mobilization @ gmail . com.

What are you waiting for? Complacency serves the old gods.


Notable submissions in this digest include:

Audio -
*Full Z5 commentaries
*Aleister Crowley Radio Documentaries
*Andrew Weil - Meditation for Optimum Health

Text -
*Allen Greenfield - Inquisition in 21st Century America
*Michael Bailey - Historical Dictionary of Witchcraft
*Henrik Bogdan - Western Esotericism and Rituals of Initiation
*Aleister Crowley - Book of the Goetia of Solomon the King
*Aleister Crowley - Liber AL vel Legis (scans from original manuscript)
*Crowley, DuQuette & Hyatt - Enochian World of Aleister Crowley
*John Dee - The Rosie Crucian Secrets
*Giovanni Pico della Mirandola - Of Being and Unity
*Harvey & Wallis - Historical Dictionary of Shamanism
*Heine & Wright - Zen Classics: Formative Texts in the History of Zen Buddhism
*Iamblichus - Theurgia or The Egyptian Mysteries
*Idries Shah - The Secret Lore of Magic
*Journal of Thelemic Studies v.2 no.1
*Robert Wang - The Secret Temple
*Frances Yates - The Occult Philosophy in the Elizabethan Age
*HOGD Outer Order Grade Materials

Video -
*Chemical Wedding
*Robert Anton Wilson - Infinity Factory
